caption:
Let’s go! I am so excited to announce that I will be fighting Oscar Duarte on December 2 

I’m back and feeling better and stronger than before. I wanted Duarte for me and for the fans. He’s tough and I’m ready to give people another show at my best weight again. 

Love you. See you December 2 on DAZN. Location and ticketing will be announced soon. @daznboxing
